9 In line 26, delete “ting”.
10 On page 9, delete lines 12 through 18 and insert:
11 “(9) All approvals of the exceptions described in subsections (3)(k) and (5)(b) of this section must
12 be made by the director of the division of the department that administers the state child welfare
13 program or the director’s designee.”.
14 In line 22, delete “6” and insert “5” and delete “and section”.
